Project 6: Food Delivery App (React Native)

Today's Focus: Complete Mobile Application Project
What I Built: Full-featured food delivery mobile app with:

Core Features:

User authentication (login/signup)

Restaurant listing with filters

Food menu browsing

Shopping cart management

Real-time order tracking

Payment integration

Order history

Push notifications

Technical Implementation:

React Native with TypeScript

Redux Toolkit for state management

React Navigation for routing

Google Maps integration

Stripe for payments

Firebase for backend

OneSignal for push notifications

FastImage for optimized images

Screens Developed:

Onboarding - App introduction

Auth - Login & Signup

Home - Restaurant listings

Restaurant Details - Menu & reviews

Cart - Order summary

Checkout - Address & payment

Order Tracking - Real-time updates

Profile - User details & history

Settings - App preferences

Advanced Features:

Offline mode with cached data

Dark/Light theme

Multi-language support

AR view for restaurants

Voice search

Dietary preference filters

Loyalty program


